# Optional — legacy one-shot bootstrap for the project picker.
# The preferred way to choose a project is via the in-app welcome screen;
# your choice is saved to ~/.openlatex/config.json. If the config file has
# no project yet and this variable is set to an existing directory, it will
# be used once and written into the config. Subsequent runs ignore it.
# PROJECT_DIR=""

# Optional — URL of the latex-api service. Defaults to http://localhost:3001.
LATEX_API_URL=""
